Run 100-agent style analysis on product data.

Uses the board meeting swarm with decision_type="creative" to analyze:
- Visual style (colors, lighting, composition)
- Brand alignment
- E-commerce best practices

The analysis runs asynchronously. Poll GET /status/\{thread_id\} for results.

Returns:
    thread_id for polling, or complete results for Level 0-1
